The '''Pineapple''' is a [[Fruits|fruit]] [[crops|crop]] that grows from [[Pineapple Seeds]] after 14 days.  It grows during Summer on [[The Farm]] or at any time on [[Ginger Island#The Farm|Ginger Island's Farm.]]

