==Quests==
*[[Caroline]] may request 100 pineapples in the [[Quests#List of Special Orders|"Island Ingredients"]] Special Order. The reward is gold equivalent to 50% of base crop price and the [[Solar Panel]] recipe.

==Recipes==
{{Recipes|header}}
{{:Tropical Curry|RecipeRow}}
{{Recipes|footer}}

==Tailoring==
Pineapple can be used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create the dyeable [[Tailoring#Pants|Farmer Pants]].  [[File:Farmer Pants.png|36px]] It can be used in [[dyeing]], serving as a yellow dye at the dye pots, located in [[Emily]]'s and [[Haley]]'s house, [[2 Willow Lane]].

